    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in poor condition and is best suited for buyers who are mechanically inclined, looking for a project car, or need basic transportation on a very tight budget. The exterior shows significant wear, including noticeable rust, multiple dents, and faded or peeling paint in several areas. The interior is heavily worn, with torn upholstery, damaged trim pieces, and general deterioration throughout the cabin. Mechanically, the car has known issues that will require attention \u2014 expect to invest in repairs to bring it to a reliable, roadworthy state. It does run and drive, but performance is inconsistent and some systems may not function as intended. This listing is priced to reflect the car's current condition honestly, and buyers should factor in repair costs when evaluating the total investment.",
      "price": 6500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 **Good Condition & Ready to Go \u2013 A Reliable Used Car You Can Count On!** Looking for a used vehicle that's been well cared for and is genuinely road-ready? This one delivers! This car is in good condition \u2014 the exterior shows only minor wear you'd expect from normal use, and the interior is clean and comfortable. Mechanically, it's been properly maintained and runs well. No major issues to hide here \u2014 just a solid, dependable vehicle at a fair price. Come take a look and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Budget-Friendly Project Car \u2014 Priced to Move! \ud83d\ude97\n\nLooking for an affordable entry point or a hands-on project? This vehicle is in poor condition and will require significant repairs before it's reliably road-ready \u2014 we want to be upfront about that! But for the right buyer \u2014 a DIY mechanic, someone with repair connections, or a parts enthusiast \u2014 there's real opportunity here at a price that reflects the work ahead. No surprises, no fluff: what you see is what you get, and the price makes room for what needs to be done. Come take a look and see if this is the project you've been waiting for! \ud83d\udd27",
      "price": 4500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition, and we want to be completely upfront with all potential buyers about its current state. The exterior shows significant wear throughout \u2014 expect multiple scratches, dents, and scuffs across various panels, with some areas showing rust or paint deterioration. The interior is similarly worn, with damaged upholstery, cracked or broken trim pieces, and general signs of heavy use over the years. Mechanically, this car has known issues and will likely require meaningful repairs to bring it to reliable daily-driver status \u2014 it is best suited for a buyer who is mechanically inclined, looking for a project vehicle, or needs basic transportation and is prepared for ongoing maintenance. There are no major safety features to highlight beyond the standard equipment it came with originally. We are pricing this vehicle accordingly to reflect its true condition, and we encourage any serious buyer to conduct a thorough inspection before purchasing.",
      "price": 3500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This car is in poor condition. It has notable mechanical issues that will require attention and repair before reliable use. The exterior shows significant wear, including visible scratches, dents, and other damage. The interior is also worn with noticeable deterioration. Sold as-is.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Here's a solid opportunity for the discerning buyer who wants dependable quality without the premium of a showroom price. This vehicle presents beautifully \u2014 clean interior, responsive mechanicals, and a well-maintained exterior that turns heads. It's been cared for by an owner who understood the value of routine upkeep, and it shows in every detail. Whether you're commuting daily or heading out on weekends, this car is ready to deliver a confident, comfortable ride from day one. Come see it in person \u2014 we're confident it will exceed your expectations.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, thanks for stopping by! I've got a really solid used car here that's been well looked after and is ready for its next adventure. She's got some normal wear from daily driving \u2014 nothing unexpected for a car this age \u2014 but mechanically she's running great and has plenty of life left in her. I've always believed in being straight with folks, and I can tell you this one is a genuinely dependable ride. Whether you're commuting, road-tripping, or just need something reliable day-to-day, this car fits the bill nicely. Come take her for a spin \u2014 I think you'll be pleasantly surprised! Priced to move and ready to go.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Rolling out of our inventory is this sharp, road-ready machine presenting in solid good condition \u2014 a genuine driver's car that's been maintained with an eye toward performance longevity. The powertrain delivers crisp throttle response with no hesitation across the rev range, and the transmission shifts with satisfying mechanical precision through every gate. Suspension geometry is dialed in, tracking true with minimal body roll \u2014 this chassis communicates confidence on both highway sweepers and technical back roads. Braking hardware shows healthy pad depth with rotors still well within spec, offering progressive, fade-resistant stopping power. Interior surfaces reflect a vehicle that's been used, not abused \u2014 functional, clean, and driver-focused. Exterior finish retains strong gloss with the kind of honest patina that tells you this car has actually been enjoyed. All major systems \u2014 cooling, electrical, drivetrain \u2014 are operating within normal parameters. Pre-purchase inspection welcomed and encouraged. A well-sorted example at a fair market price for a buyer who knows what they're looking at.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    }
  ],
